├── return.html
├── fine.html
│
├── style.css
└── script.js

 Limitations

* No backend or database integration
* Data stored only in browser (localStorage)
* Data may be lost if storage is cleared



 Future Enhancements

* Add backend integration (Node.js / Java)
* Connect to database (MySQL / MongoDB)
* Implement secure authentication
* Improve UI design
* Enable real-time data synchronization


 Conclusion

This project demonstrates a functional frontend model of a Library Management System with role-based access and essential features. It can be extended into a full-stack application with backend integration.
